  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">In a right triangle, the tangent of one of the two acute angles is <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"the fraction with numerator the square root of 3, and denominator 3\"></span></span>. What is the tangent of the other acute angle?</p>\n",
